 <TextView
         android:text="Monitoring how outdoor air quality looks like by checking the air quality
index surely minimize your exposure to outdoor air pollution, but sometimes
it is not enough. It is better to see what pollutants you are breathing, the
sources and effects in order to track the ambient air quality arround you.
We use BreezoMeter API in order to extract data about 5 pollutants: carbone monixide,
nitroge dioxide, ozone, inhalable particulate matter PM2.5 and PM10."
         app:autoSizeTextType="uniform"
         android:layout_width="284dp"
         android:layout_height="141dp" android:id="@+id/textView10"
